  <!-- ===================== LEFT HIP : 3-DOF (yaw -> roll -> pitch) ===================== -->
  <!-- The hip position offset (0.065 -0.0025 -0.055) now lives on the first (yaw) joint;
       the original orientation (rpy) and axis stay on the pitch joint so the existing
       Upper_left_leg.STL attaches exactly as before. Connector links are primitive
       cylinders (no STL needed). NOTE: yaw axis = Z (vertical), roll axis = X (forward);
       verify/flip in RViz if the sense looks wrong for your build. -->
